    <body style="font-family:微软雅黑; margin-top:5%;">
    	<div class="container" style="">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12" align="center">
                    <h3 class="display-3" style="color:#FF0000">夺宝邀请用户玩法简介</h3><br>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
                    <p class="lead" style="font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;邀请用户玩法旨在为用户提供交流的方式，邀请好友共同参加抽奖活动，可以为彼此双方赢得额外的夺宝码，提升中奖几率。现就详细的邀请玩法说明如下：</p>
                    <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.每位用户每期抽奖至多可邀请<mark>20位</mark>好友。</p>
                    <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.每位用户每期抽奖至多可接受<mark>20位</mark>好友邀请。</p>
                    <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.每次邀请好友，需要支付<mark>10 SZB</mark>。好友一旦接受了邀请，支付的<mark>10 SZB</mark>自动转换为一个额外的夺宝码。但是如果到期好友未接受您的邀请，支付的<mark>10 SZB</mark>将退还至您的账户。</p>
                    <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.好友在接到邀请的时候，需要支付<mark>10 SZB</mark>才能确认邀请，支付的<mark>10 SZB</mark>自动转换为一个额外的夺宝码。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12" align="center">
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="display-3" style="color:#FF0000">具体操作实例：</h4><br>
                        <p class="lead" style="font-weight: bold;">进入抽奖页面，其中<mark>“立即抢购”</mark>和<mark>“查看夺宝号”</mark>与普通夺宝玩法功能一致。</p>
                        <img src="../img/lottery_invite_01.jpg" class="img-rounded img-responsive center-block" style="border-bottom: groove;">
                    </div><br>
                    <div>
                        <p class="lead" style="font-weight: bold;">点击<mark>“邀请用户”</mark>，填写用户itcode即可发出邀请。</p>
                        <img src="../img/lottery_invite_02.jpg" class="img-rounded img-responsive center-block" style="border-bottom: groove;">
                    </div><br>
                    <div>
                        <p class="lead" style="font-weight: bold;">点击<mark>“查看邀请”</mark>，可查看所有邀请您的邀请，点击<mark>“接受邀请”</mark>即可接受该用户的邀请。</p>
                        <img src="../img/lottery_invite_03.jpg" class="img-rounded img-responsive center-block" style="border-bottom: groove;">
                    </div><br>
                    <div>
                        <p class="lead" style="font-weight: bold;">再次点击<mark>“查看邀请”</mark>，即可看到上步接受的邀请状态变为已接受。</p>
                        <img src="../img/lottery_invite_04.jpg" class="img-rounded img-responsive center-block" style="border-bottom: groove;">
                    </div><br>
                    <div>
                        <p class="lead" style="font-weight: bold;">点击<mark>“查看夺宝号”</mark>，即可查看接受邀请所获得的奖励夺宝码。</p>
                        <img src="../img/lottery_invite_05.jpg" class="img-rounded img-responsive center-block" style="border-bottom: groove;">
                    </div><br>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12" align="center">
                    <br><p class="lead" style="font-weight: bold;">快来邀请好友一同参加吧！</p><br>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
